<img src="http://img.tongji.linezing.com/3379661/tongji.gif" border="0" /></description>
                <link>http://williamlfang.github.com/cn/2009/02/20/till-the-end/</link>
                <guid>http://williamlfang.github.com/cn/2009/02/20/till-the-end/</guid>
